{"tid":229173,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"20秒遭徐曉冬KO     太極宗師：若用內力怕他會死...","createTime":"2017-05-04T12:07:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-04T12:55:54.000Z","uid":58099,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"18a76986d87907f79e2fb909a6c0bf054467c0d2","tid":229173,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T12:07:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/v22674bkn-2017_03br63.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Fv22674bkn-2017_03br63.jpg&h=291169a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日前中國「格鬥狂人」徐曉冬20秒KO號稱「太極宗師」魏雷的影片，引發一場武林爭端。魏雷表示，當時他穿著新鞋，而且地板材質易滑，才會跌倒，又稱自己若使用內力，可能會讓徐曉冬喪命。<br />\n<br />\n魏雷表示，當時比賽時穿著新膠底鞋，場地也是橡膠地面，往後退的時候就摔倒了，他無奈地說，「我需要太多解釋嗎？」<br />\n魏雷認為，自己有打倒徐曉冬的實力，只是沒有施展開來，內家拳的內力不能對每個人用，害怕自己的內力會打死徐曉東，要進派出所了。魏雷說，這是遵循師父的教導不濫用武力，要是真用內力打，可能幾天之後就出人命。"},{"pid":"792fbee3477de5ca87019185cbd254392959fa7f","tid":229173,"uid":9548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T12:08:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2001537e57ef37a1f1b3e51752565d18f48dc433","tid":229173,"uid":54431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T12:09:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4330994556b44f785bd7cf3991cb9ad83907f7ad","tid":229173,"uid":62028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T12:12:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5baa9d2d6bbf1fbaac999ae546fd60e5a35da41b","tid":229173,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T12:12:55.000Z","msg":"馬後炮大師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c9dc9aeb8bce24fd94676f1d0d351eb04c6e3be","tid":229173,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T12:13:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/ass